<a name="EOF"></a>

```go
const (
    // Single-character tokens.
    EOF TokenType = iota
    ERROR
    LEFT_PAREN
    RIGHT_PAREN
    LEFT_BRACE
    RIGHT_BRACE
    LEFT_BRACKET
    RIGHT_BRACKET
    PERCENT
    COLON
    COMMA
    DOT
    MINUS
    PLUS
    SEMICOLON
    SLASH
    STAR
    QMARK
    // One or two character tokens.
    BANG
    BANG_EQUAL
    EQUAL
    EQUAL_EQUAL
    GREATER
    GREATER_EQUAL
    LESS
    LESS_EQUAL
    TEMPLATE_LEFT_BRACE
    TEMPLATE_RIGHT_BRACE
    AND
    OR
    // Literals.
    IDENTIFIER
    STRING
    NUMBER
    TEXT

    FALSE
    TRUE
    NIL
)
```
